        <mxCell id="chat-text" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontFamily=Courier New;fontSize=10;spacingTop=2;spacingLeft=4;" value="&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;ok then :D&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;@everyone&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt; say hello to &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;@mergepudall&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;@mello3&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;hallo... i remember reading the irc rfc by hand just to figure out how to greet a user... now it&#39;s all just bloated javascript... so tired...&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;mclark &amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;Omet I&#39;m fixing CI on my Ignore PR — did you try the artboard demo?&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;jast rc &amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt; @mello3&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;not yet, leaving for later, jsh still need stuff writing :D&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;Migo &amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;dang job always taking up time :( #1 priority tho&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;out &amp;gt;&amp;gt; @&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;we are busy today! :D thats what i love to see&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;water your tree!&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;sloom0 &amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;yyyeah I hate escape strings dont know how they work at all&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;out &amp;gt;&amp;gt; @&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;send you a DM :| question about the broken audpip&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;mclark &amp;gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;slime was a late theme now&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#302010&quot;&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;mclark&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt; ha&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#6688AA&quot;&gt;https://wikitext.info/sp/NbG0MD24pPflcUBCImage.png&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#C08030&quot;&gt;@sloom0&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#805020&quot;&gt;#i pipelines and themes... we used to just edit .htaccess in vim and run make... Now you need a whole cloud infrastructure just to change a color... whatever...&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
